data.title: James 'Jimmy' McNulty Quotes
data.meta_description: Discover and share the most famous quotes by James 'Jimmy' McNulty.
data.text:
You don’t look at what you did before, you do the same s*** all over.

Who in this f***ing unit is gonna catch me? Most of the guys up here couldn’t catch the clap in a Mexican whorehouse.[to Bunk]

What kind of detective would I be if I couldn’t track a white woman in Baltimore, right?

They can chew you up, but they gotta spit you back out.

There were two of them. I was outnumbered.[about the two hookers in the sting operation]

Lying to the wife’s easy. It’s looking your kid in the eye that’s the hard part.

Let’s go home.[the last line of the series]

I wonder what it feels like to work in a real f***ing police department.
